I LOVE THIS PLACE AND THIS PIZZA!  I always create my own of the Pesto Sauce, Sausage, Pine Nuts (Extra Pine Nuts), with Fresh Mozzarella Cheese and Parmesan Cheese.  The only problem I have is there is not one across the street from where I live!  Priced well for the quality of food you receive and there is always extra to take home, but truthfully I have to make the effort not to eat the entire pie in one sitting!

Tell them Chef Sandra sent you